{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Raële : Es ef-\nmu zaür Deewa Zihnischanahin\nar manni Mahfu zihniufsees/ un\narri usivarrejuti / un nofauze\nwinna Wahrdü Nawtalis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Lea redfeja / ka ta\nbij mittejupees dsemideht / tad\nachme ta arridsan fawu Kalponi\nSilpu / un dewe to Jehkabam\npar Seetwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Silpa / Leas Kalpone/\ndsemdeja Jehkabam Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea: tur nahk\nveens Pulks / un nofauze winna\nWahrdü Gads.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Silpa / Leas Kalpone\ndsemdeja Jehkabam to ohtru\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea:Lab man/\notahs Meitas turrehs man laimt-\nu/ un ta nofauze winna Wahrd-\nu Ahsers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ruhbens gabje Kwée-\nchu- Ptanujama Laikā/un atradde\nDudaim Laukā / un atneffe tohs\nfai fawai Mahtei / un Raële\nazzija uhs Leit / dohd man jelle\nto tawa Dehta Dudaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna fazzija us to :\nzrr ta weena masa Leeta / ka tu\nmannu Wihru effi atnehmufi/\nn tu gribbi arridsan manna Deh-\na Dudaim nemt ? tad fazzija\nRaële / tapehz buhs tam scho\nNakti pee terw gullek par tawa\nDehla Dudaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Jehlabs Wakkara\nno Lauka nahze/ tad isgahje Lea\ntam pretti / un fazzija: pee man\nbuhs terw nahkt / jo es ejinn terw\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ar Maffu faderrejusi par man-\nna Dehla Dudaim / un wiꞥſch\ngulleja pee tahs tanni Nakti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews paflansija to\nLeit / un ta tappe gruhta / un\ndsemdeja Jehkabam to peektu\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea : Deews\nirr man to maffajs / ka es man-\nnam Wihram mannu Kalponi\nefinu dewuji/ un ta nofauze win-\nna Wahrdü Jhsafchars.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lea tappe atkat gruh-\nta/ un dsemdeja Jehkabam to feſ-\ntu Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Lea : Deews\nirr man apdahwanajs ar labbu\nDahwanu / scho Brihdi peedsih-\nwohs man mans Wihrs/ tapehz/\nka es winnam fetch Dehlus eſ-\nmu dsemdejti/ un nofauze winna\nWahrdü Sebulons.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz to dsemdeja win-\nna weenu Meitu/un nofauze win-\nnas Wahrdü Dina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews atgahdajahsus\nRaëli / un Deews paflausija\nwinan/ un dartija winnu aug-\nligu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna tappe gruhta/\nun dsemdeja weenn Dehlu / un\nfazzija : DEews irr mannu Ap-\nsineeklu no mannim atnehmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta nofauze winna\nWahrdü Jahseps / fazzidana:\nLard tas KUNGS man apdah-\nwana wehl ar zittu Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notieke / kad Raële\nJahsepu bij dsemdejust / fazzija\nJehlabs us Lahbanu : atlaid\nman/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
